prompt: Inside a sun-drenched, glass-walled botanical conservatory filled with towering tropical plants. A Middle Eastern female professional in her late 20s, wearing a sharp royal blue blazer (primary brand color), stands at a high rustic potting bench. Instead of plants, the table is covered in a strategic layout of printed team photos and a large yearly planning calendar. She is holding a marker, thoughtfully circling a date for the next refresh. The scene juxtaposes the organic, growing environment with structured corporate strategy. Deep green foliage surrounds her (secondary color), and a bright azure notebook (accent color) rests nearby.
